   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-accepting-acceptted" mid="85" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I see. Well, he's a well-respected bishop in this society. It's our bad to have thought that we could convince the adventurers easily.<BR>Now the best way would be to spoil the bishop's plans while you pretend to help him. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-1-a" mid="88" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Luckily he is not suspicious of you. Why don't you try persuading him like what you did to Elena?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-1-b" mid="89" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9611_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Yes. Why don't you tell him to stop resurrecting Serpentra when you bring Rose to him?<BR>I don't know what his intentions are for resurrecting Serpentra, but his main goal would be to get the Prophet in his hands.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-1-c" mid="90" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>But I can't let Rose fall into his hands.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-2" mid="91" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9611_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I'm not saying we should really give her to him. We're going to lie just like he did. Stop Serpentra's resurrection for now then ignore him later.<BR>Let's think about other ways to reveal the bishop's identity to others. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-" mid="92" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>Sea Dragon Serpentra will be resurrected soon. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1894_light_pole-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1894_light_pole-1-" mid="93" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$???$<BR>….<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Someone seems to have held rituals here. You don't know exactly what kind of ritual it was.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-2" image="QN_Npc_Bishop.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-2-" mid="94" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Go and try persuading the bishop.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-a" mid="95" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>The resurrection is going smoothly as planned. The documents about dragons that the Ancients recorded down were particularly useful.<BR>Now wait a little while for a good show.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-b" mid="96" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Do you really need to resurrect Serpentra?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-c" mid="97" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>There's nothing else I can do since I can't get the Prophet out because of the Gold Dragon. <BR>But there's nothing for you to be worried about. You just have to follow my orders. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-d" mid="98" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What's more important than resurrecting Serpentra is to get the Prophet, isn't it?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-e" mid="99" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>Well, of course. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Bishop Ignacio smiles warmly.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-f" mid="100" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Actually I could enter the nest from some time ago by chance. I'll bring the Prophet to you in any way I can so please stop resurrecting Serpentra.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-g" mid="101" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>There's no reason for me to resurrect Sea Dragon Serpentra if you would do that for me. But it's too late. Those who were following my orders have already finished the ritual to resurrect Sea Dragon Serpentra.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-3" mid="102" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>Oh, don't look so sad. I have a way. <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Bishop Ignacio gives you a small vial.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-3" image="QW_47.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-3-" mid="103" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>Take this to the <FONT color=#a82424>Ruins of Lost Time</FONT> where the ritual took place and sprinkle it there. The spell that was going to resurrect Serpentra will be cancelled.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1894_light_pole-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1894_light_pole-3-a" mid="104" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$???$<BR>….<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(A ritual seems to have been taken place here. There are scales on the floor. This seems to be the place where Serpentra resurrected.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1894_light_pole-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1894_light_pole-4" mid="105" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I guess I can pour it here.<BR>(Pour the potion that Ignacio to the very last drop.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1894_light_pole-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1894_light_pole-4-" mid="106" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$???$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The potion seeps into the ground without a trace.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-a" mid="107" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR>What are you doing here? Hey, this looks like signs of a ritual!!<BR>Are you still helping the Dragon Followers?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-b" mid="108" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>No, this is to prevent Serpentra from resurrecting.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-c" mid="109" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR>What are you talking about? Serpentra has already resurrected and Saint Haven is in chaos.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-d" mid="110" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What? It resurrected?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-e" mid="111" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya${sound:npc_Suriya_9611_qu_01.ogg}<BR>So I guess it's the Dragon Followers who resurrected Serpentra. <BR>Do you realise how rash you were?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-f" mid="112" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR>Now Saint Haven is in trouble. I was about to leave this place too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-g" mid="113" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Leave? Where are you going? Are you taking my villagers with you?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-h" mid="114" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya${sound:npc_Suriya_9611_qu_02.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Suriya looks gloomy.)</FONT><BR>No. I'm going to Lotus Marsh. I'm going there partly because of your villagers.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-i" mid="115" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>You're not taking my villagers? So you're trying to save your own life?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-j" mid="116" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR>Phew... I can't hide it from you anymore. We tried our best to save everyone.<BR>But from the moment we rescued them, no one was in a good state like you. There was a plague too and... It's not like we wanted to sit around watching our fellow hybrids die too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-k" mid="117" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>They... died? Who? How many?!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-l" mid="118" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR>Do you remember what I told you when you suddenly collapsed? They started to fall one by one like that.<BR>I think their symptoms are showing on you as well. It's just that it's progressing slower.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-m" mid="119" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I don't care about me. So how many of my villagers died?!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-n" mid="120" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Suriya avoids looking at you.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-o" mid="121" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Don't tell me... They're all dead?! Why didn't you tell me earlier? I was finally starting to trust you! Why!!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-p" mid="122" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya${sound:npc_Suriya_9611_qu_03.ogg}<BR>I'm sorry. We're going to Lotus Marsh because... we want to bury your villagers in their homeland. When we get there, we're going to find the laboratory that made your villagers like that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-q" mid="123" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That's not a laboratory. It's a medical center. </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-4-r" mid="124" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR>Do you still believe that? All the documents there can save the lives of other hybrids. It would be good if you can tell me where it is.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-4-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-5" mid="125" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Of course I still believe it! I trust the people who used to treat me more than I trust you!<BR>Don't you go to that medical center. I won't forgive you if you do!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-5-a" mid="126" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Suriya$<BR>I guess I shouldn't have told you about it. Anyway, I need to go.<BR>You should stop wasting your time on Serpentra or whatever and think about saving your own life. If you don't want to die, that is.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1895_suriya-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Left_Suriya.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1895_suriya-5-" mid="127" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I wasn't going to talk to you anymore either! I'm going back to my master.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-5-a" mid="128" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Have you heard the news? The bishop has finally created trouble!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-5-b" mid="129" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Master, I'm going to die.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-5-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-5-c" mid="130" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I'm very worried about the danger we're in too. But being concerned only about your own life is not the right thing to do for a martial artist. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-5-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-5-d" mid="131" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Xiaolong preaches noisily. Tell him about what Suriya said.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-5-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-5-e" mid="132" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I see. The reason why the symptoms are appearing slower on you could be because of my kung fu which stopped aging for me.<BR>And that also means we still have hope. Don't forget that you're still alive.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1861_shaolong-5-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1861_shaolong-5-f" mid="133" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What hope?<BR>I'm going to die soon, Saint Haven is going to be crushed by Serpentra, and the bishop is going to get what he wants.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
